        "attrs": {
          "textAlign": null
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Our goal is that every UUPG will have at least 144 people from around the world praying for them 10 minutes a day. This will give us 24-hour prayer coverage for every one of these UUPGs."
